Watchlist

Where to Watch

After he is dumped by his girlfriend for ducking out of a fight, a hapless Old West farmhand learns how to shoot from an outlaw's wife in this riotous comedy. The pair eventually fall in love, but her husband wants to challenge him to a showdown.
